He co-edited the following collections of essays:
*{{cite book |title= Beyond the Witch Trials: Witchcraft and Magic in Enlightenment Europe|editor1-first= Owen |editor1-last= Davies |editor2-first= Willem |editor2-last= de Blécourt |year= 2004 |publisher=Manchester University Press |isbn=978-0-7190-6660-3 |oclc= 56344687 }} *{{cite book |title= Witchcraft Continued: Popular Magic in Modern Europe |editor1-first= Willem |editor1-last= de Blécourt |editor2-first= Owen |editor2-last= Davies|year= 2004 |publisher= Manchester University Press |isbn=978-0-7190-6658-0 |oclc= 56465533 }}
He has also written numerous articles on the same subject in various history and folklore journals.
